title: The Dew of Their Youth
author: Crockett, S. R. (Samuel Rutherford)
snippet: For did shenot come of the best blood of the Westland Whigs, great-granddaughterof that Bell of Whiteside, kinsman of Kenmure's, who was shot by Lagon the moor of Kirkconnel, near to the Lynn through which the Tarfffoams white?
